// Teacher-provided PDF drum lessons, extracted from /uploads tab PDFs.
//
// Count-row lessons are parsed as deterministic patterns. PDFs without explicit
// count rows are retained as probabilistic visual imports: their step-level
// `probability` values represent parse confidence and their notes are marked TBR.
// The app stays static and has no runtime PDF dependency.

